timeline
    title Evolution of Data Architectures
    1990s-2000s : Gen 1 - Data Warehouse
                : Teradata, Oracle, SQL Server
                : Structured data only
                : Great for BI, expensive
    2010s : Gen 2 - Data Lake
          : Hadoop, S3, ADLS
          : Cheap storage, any format
          : No ACID - Data Swamp
    2020s : Gen 3 - Lakehouse
          : Delta Lake, Iceberg, Hudi
          : Cheap + ACID + Governance
          : BI + ML + Streaming
